Tica: Ouch~ That hurt!
Dagger: Grrrrr! Watch where you're going, brat!

Tica: Eh? Do you also have presents in that big bag too?

Tica: You have a bag that looks just like mine, so I thought you were going to deliver presents too~
Dagger: You're delivering presents?
Tica: That's right~ I'm gonna hand out the presents in this bag to everyone!
Dagger: Everyone!?
Tica: Recently, it seems like everybody is feeling down. Therefore, I decided to give everyone "Tica's Custom-made Surprise Christmas Gift!"
Tica: When they get my present, everyone will be in a better mood!
Dagger: That's lot of presents. Do you have time to deliver them all?
Tica: Crap, wasted too much time on those damn shrooms. Time's running short~

Tica: This one's for you~
